{"tid":1364934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel《上氣》：將反派 「傅滿洲」（Manchu) 改名為 「滿大人）(Mandarin). 內地網民：辱華！！","createTime":"2019-07-25T13:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T13:25:36.000Z","uid":226548,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e24b5ae4149dca5f712e9c70b07ac7c5ff00600e","tid":1364934,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3061251/org/c93071e5f3c5bc0f12b90fe75c0ae02b.jpg/9mxBJ0RfxAJbHuDsAnbkrXBBzAmqZvrQ_ivpIv4r6SI?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3061251%2Forg%2Fc93071e5f3c5bc0f12b90fe75c0ae02b.jpg%2F9mxBJ0RfxAJbHuDsAnbkrXBBzAmqZvrQ_ivpIv4r6SI%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=5b9c7286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMarvel於聖地牙哥動漫展公布，其首部華人英雄電影《Shang-Chi: The Legend of the Ten Rings》（直譯：《上氣：十環傳奇》）中，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反派「滿大人」</span></strong>一角由梁朝偉出演，消息傳後不少亞洲粉絲都直言十分期待，但卻同時觸怒了許多內地網民，狠批梁朝偉「辱華」，稱Marvel漫畫中，滿大人的角色就是取材自<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「傅滿洲」</span></strong>，是西方歧視的華人、「黃禍」的代表人物，「有心考慮中國粉絲的話，避嫌都不懂嗎？」、「梁朝偉想躋身國際想瘋了嗎？」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">歧視 滿洲人 = 辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"75abe09ece8f61dad3296fe61cb8fde39f364eb1","tid":1364934,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:09:38.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/354454/marvel-上氣-梁朝偉演滿大人-內地影迷網上怒罵-辱華\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C%2F354454%2Fmarvel-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%A3-%E6%A2%81%E6%9C%9D%E5%81%89%E6%BC%94%E6%BB%BF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%BA-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%B1%E8%BF%B7%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%80%92%E7%BD%B5-%E8%BE%B1%E8%8F%AF&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6dTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=a419afc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/354454/marvel-上氣-梁朝偉演滿大人-內